<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns hat Jobs Kapfer,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>schreib<ex>er</ex></expan>, wol gesagt etlich rede, die ewr gnade im
                        befolhen <expan>hab</expan> an uns zu <expan>werbe<ex>n</ex></expan> als von
                        des newen zolls <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, den man in dem lande zu
                                <expan>Franke<ex>n</ex></expan> untersteen meynt zu nemen etc. Also
                                <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                            <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>schreib<ex>er</ex></expan> Jobs zu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>, dem wir befolhen
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>zu red<ex>en</ex></expan>, und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                        gnade mit fleiss, was <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> in <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> zu disem mal von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an ewr gnade <expan>w<ex>er</ex>be</expan>,
                        daz ir in darinn <expan>gnedikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>hörn</expan>, im des <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>gelawbe<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>gunstikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> von
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>fertig<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet. Als etc. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
